text.__SUMMARY__: Common names: Savu python.Liasis mackloti savuensis is a python subspecies found in Indonesia. It is known by the locals as sanca mata putih (white-eyed python).
text.Distribution and habitat: The type locality given is "Savu Id." (=Sawoe, Indonesia).
